&lt;li&gt;Adjustable stroke option, +2 to -25 mm adjustment range&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hollow piston rod option&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Auto switch capable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Air-hydro type available&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

